                  </persName>
            . I am a porter. I was passing St. Dunstan's church, and saw Webb following the prisoner, who had the boxes - he dropped them in the middle of the passage. A gentleman stopped him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am innocent.</p>
